title: Los Angeles Magazine
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20111225034026im_/http:/typophile.com/files/LosAngelesMagazineLogo_5394.png)

Does anyone know the typeface used for Los Angeles Magazine's logo. I know it was design by Jim Parkinson but any idea what font was used. Thanks in advance
author: pcshakur

comments.content:
